<Project>

  <!-- Deliberately empty, and deliberately here: it stops MSBuild walking up to the repo-root
       Directory.Build.props for anything vendored under third_party/. Third-party source is built on its
       own csproj's terms — not the app's version stamp, EnforceCodeStyleInBuild, GenerateDocumentationFile
       or IDE0005-as-error rules (.editorconfig), none of which a foreign codebase was written to satisfy.
       The paired third_party/.editorconfig (root = true) stops the style cascade for the same reason. -->

</Project>
